  <brief_title>Prevalence of Diabetes Mellitus Among Patients Treated With Atypical and Conventional Antipsychotics</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prevalence and Incidence of Diabetes Mellitus Among Patients Treated With Atypical and Conventional Antipsychotics</official_title>
